Israel, Jerold H.; Kamisar, Yale; LaFave, Wayne R. Criminal Procedure and the Constitution: Leading Supreme Court Cases and Introductory Text. St. Paul, MN: West Publishing. 2003. ISBN 0-314-14669-5. 


